casebody.data:
STATE of New Jersey, Plaintiff-Respondent,
v.
Donell J. ANDERSON, Defendant-Petitioner. C-269 Sept. Term 2018
081148 Supreme Court of New Jersey. November 2, 2018

ORDER

A petition for certification of the judgment in A-001798-16 having been submitted to this Court, and the Court having considered the same;

It is ORDERED that the petition for certification is granted and the matter is summarily remanded to the Superior Court, Appellate Division for reconsideration in light of State v. Rainlin Vasco , 235 N.J. 365 , 195 A.3d 839 (2018).
